headline: Disney target raised at Guggenheim on sports, parks momentum
summary: Investing.com -- Guggenheim raised its price target on Walt Disney (NYSE:DIS) Co to $140 from $120 on stronger-than-expected trends across sports advertising, theme parks, and progress on cost-cutting as the company pushes toward a more unified streaming strategy.
